@{
    ViewBag.Title = "Home Page";
}


<div id="section1">
    <div class="title" id="title1"></div>
    <div id="image1" class="img-rounded visible-md visible-lg"></div>
    <div class="copy" id="text1">
        <h4 class="title">SAGIP</h4>
        <p>SAGIP is a cloud-based Weather Forecast System of Rice Watch and Action Network’s(R1) Local Government partners to support livelihood decision-making and disaster risks reduction initiative. The system was developed with the support of Greenpeace in partnership with Rice Watch and Action Network(R1) to support CrFS adopting LGUs.</p>
        <br /><br />
        <h4 class="title">Farmer</h4>
        <p>Receives weather advisories from the Local Government via Short Messaging Service(SMS). Weather advisory recipient may send feedback to the Local Government about the forecast via Short Messaging Service(SMS). Everything is made possible by SAGIP System. </p>
    </div>
</div>
<div id="divider3"></div>
<div id="section2">
    <div class="title" id="title2"></div>
    <div id="banner" class="visible-lg"></div>
    <div class="copy" id="column1">
        <h4 class="title">Local Government</h4>
        <p>Disseminates received information to farmers and communities. The information will be sent via Short Messaging Service(SMS) to every registered mobile number within SAGIP System.</p>
        <br />
        <h4 class="title">Weather Station</h4>
        <p>Issues information to Local Government on weather-related hazards, potential community/livelihood impacts and farm-weather advisories or risks management recommendation.</p>
    </div>
</div>


